	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["config"] = {
					["color"] = {
						0.58823531866074,
						0.68627452850342,
						0.96470588445663,
						1.0,
					},
				},
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/Dialog03SceneBG/bg_room_14_beforefire.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]卸去一身的疲惫后，云无月回到房间，坐在窗边的座位上出神。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "76C71B6D4B3B3A7B44E351AE51047148",
		["guid_str"] = "ugQbdnPb",
		["id"] = 3,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["config"] = {
					["color"] = {
						0.58823531866074,
						0.68627452850342,
						0.96470588445663,
						1.0,
					},
				},
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/Dialog03SceneBG/bg_room_14_beforefire.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]窗台上的盆栽在悉心照顾下总算恢复了些许生机，之前还是无精打采，\n\n现在却已经冒出了几个花骨朵，一副迎风待绽的景象。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
		["guid"] = "A3735E454C603EFFA74370A7D3904395",
		["guid_str"] = "DiJnHWP3",
		["id"] = 4,
	},
	{
		["bg_info"] = {
			{
				["config"] = {
					["color"] = {
						0.58823531866074,
						0.68627452850342,
						0.96470588445663,
						1.0,
					},
				},
				["path"] = "interface/resource/Game/Dialog03SceneBG/bg_room_14_beforefire.png",
			},
			{
			},
		},
		["caption_info"] = {
			["b_use_mask"] = true,
			["mask_alpha"] = 0.5,
			["text"] = "[size 17]想到在即将到来的夏天应该就能见到它盛开的样子，云无月不由得多了几分期待。",
			["text_align"] = "center",
		},
